# -*- mode: snippet -*-
# name: babel-shell
# key: babel-sh
# --
* Shell Script
:PROPERTIES:
:header-args: :tangle ${1:~/bin/`(file-name-nondirectory (file-name-sans-extension (buffer-file-name)))`}
:header-args+: :comments org :mkdirp yes
:header-args+: :shebang "# -*- mode: sh -*-"
:header-args+: :tangle-mode (identity #o644)
:END:

  Create the script by tangling it with: =C-c C-v t=
